{"tid":1505362,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"技術燃搞放映","createTime":"2019-08-25T13:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T17:43:03.000Z","uid":272017,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1e87ade3aadbe30b860178fc01b09ac0bb4d2646","tid":1505362,"uid":272017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"來點自我介紹， 我是一個不折不扣的宅。<br />\n我本來想整呢D: (圖是別人的，貼自家的作品會直接導致被起底)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QOoMmvW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQOoMmvW.jpg&h=ca1eb27c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府搞到我要整呢d:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HEQu3Km.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHEQu3Km.jpg&h=3bba86fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>目標：</strong></ins><br />\n可以插usb 電即播、快速打開、可快速走起、同埋低價的放映裝置<br />\n可以一個場放多個，播不同主題的 (黑警為重點、五大訴求為重點等)<br />\n零件的來源多樣化。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>材料： (443 HKD)</ins></strong><br />\nRaspberry Pi Zero (70 HKD )<br />\n16 GB Micro SD Card (35 HKD)<br />\n無殼5寸 mon, 5V 供電 支持hdmi 輸入 (180 hkd)<br />\nHdmi 線 （鴨記最平的那種，20HKD)<br />\n10000 mAH 尿袋 (79 HKD)<br />\nMICRO USB電源線電腦喇叭 （19 HKD)<br />\n鋁角 （10 HKD)<br />\n鴨記手機架（30HKD)<br />\nM3 縲絲/絲帽<br />\nM3 銅柱<br />\nM5 自攻縲絲<br />\n<strong><ins>其他可再用物料:</ins></strong><br />\n 1. 電腦<br />\n 2. 讀咭機<br />\n 3. USB OTG CABLE<br />\n 4. USB 手指<br />\n 5. 電批<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>作業系統:</ins></strong><br />\nRaspberry-Slideshow<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.binaryemotions.com/digital-signage/raspberry-slideshow/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.binaryemotions.com%2Fdigital-signage%2Fraspberry-slideshow%2F&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=f551634c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.binaryemotions.com/digital-signage/raspberry-slideshow/</a><br />\n這個系統其實是一個改動過的LINUX，只是做以下兩件事:<br />\n 1. 如果開機時找到有USB手指，就把USB手指中的所有影片和圖片取代內部記憶體中的東西<br />\n 2. 播放內部記憶體中的影片和圖片<br />\n<br />\n正正因為如此簡單，所以才合用。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>制作步驟：</ins></strong><br />\n其實沒什麼特別，只是把東西用自攻縲絲/M3 銅柱固定在鋁角上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BK1VeRH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBK1VeRH.jpg&h=21b8bb1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以及直觀地駁線。(要些少銲接能力)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U5JAeRj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU5JAeRj.png&h=760ec403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>內容:</ins></strong><br />\n以6~7分鐘內可以看完的片段為主。主要面向一些行過連農牆/橋的中間派人士。<br />\n<ins>57 studio</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCJDEPjKYyvfcwRYGePAy4Iw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCJDEPjKYyvfcwRYGePAy4Iw&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=280f200c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCJDEPjKYyvfcwRYGePAy4Iw</a><br />\n<ins>其他片源</ins>:<br />\n中英字幕: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2KpIbsA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KpIbsA&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=5bdfbc1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2KpIbsA</a><br />\n純中字幕: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2YXU1lY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YXU1lY&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=77028f7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2YXU1lY</a><br />\n純英字幕: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2OQyTu6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OQyTu6&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=a00b575a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2OQyTu6</a><br />\n直播/冇字幕: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2yPNCdE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2yPNCdE&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=deff393a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2yPNCdE</a><br />\n18區 連儂放映會:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/652678141881787/about/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F652678141881787%2Fabout%2F&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=6cf89c09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/652678141881787/about/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>事後檢討:</ins></strong><br />\n<ins>正面: </ins><br />\n測試過後，電力耐用程度沒的說。播了7小時10000 mAH 尿袋還有50%電。<br />\nRASPBERRY PI ZERO 方案夠輕便，而且比用手機平得多。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>負面:</ins><br />\n動手能力要高。<br />\n諷刺的是我成功地踢走手機這個高價東西，但5V HDMI MON 的價錢就一點都不便宜。<br />\n全套都要443 HKD，可能轉去用電子相架一類的比較好。(不過現在很難找)"},{"pid":"081645bad48e552991eae49feee6288bf54be5fb","tid":1505362,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a262c664da090ef21dd3494ff641a65b2b51e74d","tid":1505362,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:53:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d780c2bbe76eef3e7339d689b7707b3f03079f03","tid":1505362,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ce4aa9097aecd7d5654891c1cda2849e350187","tid":1505362,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ae73309edcf2177810a62de9dfbcadffb5ab31","tid":1505362,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c50f42bdfe13d516740c37de06f3182c2e8ca4","tid":1505362,"uid":308041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:12:12.000Z","msg":"核彈要靠你了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />